{"tid":2302151,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp個備份回復訊息係全世界最垃圾既功能","createTime":"2020-11-27T01:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T06:07:32.000Z","uid":241868,"like":103,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebada37f7c09aad8e90d2c26a6775e5ae0de0c8","tid":2302151,"uid":241868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:54:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我Android 轉會入iOS 要整備份Transfer Data 落iPhone度<br />\n好啦 一切順利 做曬backup <br />\n做到Data Transfer 個software 要我del左個新版wtsapp<br />\n係舊版wtsapp回復備份<br />\n<br />\n呢度就開始卡關<br />\n試左勁多次都同我講無法回復備份<br />\n好 咁我裝返新版試, 頂你個肺 一樣回復唔到<br />\n但有得撳現在回復備份 （屌你咁我岩岩回復緊啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撳左之後 情況火上加油！本身load到30%一下跌到10%<br />\n再升上去100%，然後再跌去44%, 咁宜家姐係點呀？？？彈出彈入玩9我呀？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者我望住個數跳左半個鐘 都未回復完，我決定重試再黎過, 然後個話我試得太多次 要7個鐘之先可以再用SMS send驗證碼<br />\n<br />\nFine! 用語音囉！咁次做完research ，將wtsapp個folder copy埋落SD card，Del左Google driver個備份，應該實冇死<br />\n<br />\n然後回復到44%冇郁過15分鐘，我就去恰陣<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">然後！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>1個鐘後！！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">仲係44%！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我頂唔順，重新黎過<br />\n仆你個街，SMS要6個鐘後，語音驗證碼2個鐘後<br />\n<br />\n我宜家企撚左係度，收唔到任何wtsapp<br />\n<br />\n到底wtsapp個回復訊息功能係用黎做咩"},{"pid":"abd7d3d9e4d7bc889e38eeebf36265f51ee8eca2","tid":2302151,"uid":37796,"like":24,"dislike":87,"score":-63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"係ios 封閉姐<br />\n關whatsapp咩事"},{"pid":"b8210fc441cd8b97913f8a268433614cc31da858","tid":2302151,"uid":150033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"兩部機係咪更新到最新 <br />\n同試試取消連結apple account 熄機重開再登入<br />\n<br />\n利申 8轉12時搞左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081814086b92db4